name: DUMMY KEYTYPE

column.comment: UWO is Unity Media work order, source attributes are WONUM,UMREGION,WOARUN,WOTYC

column.comment:
UCUST is unity media customer and source attributes are 
WORDM.WOCU# , UMREGION

column.name: KEYTYPE_UWOSTT
column.comment: UWOSTT is Unity media work order status and source attribute is WOSTT

column.name: KEYTYPE_CLOB_DUM
column.comment: CLOB is cable Line of business and source value is 'cable'

column.name: KEYTYPE_CWOREL_DUM

column.name: KEYTYPE_CSF_DUM
column.comment: Cable sales agent code.

column.name: KEYTYPE_UWODSRC_DUM
column.comment:
Interface from unity media source is WORDD(work order detail),
UWOD represents source attributes  WDWO#, UMREGION, WDARUN, WDSRC and WDSTYP

column.name: KEYTYPE_UWODSRCACT_DUM
column.comment: UWODSRCACT is Unity media work order detail service action  and represent source attributes WDWO#, UMREGION, WDARUN, WDSRC, WDSTYP and action basis of derivation.

column.name: KEYTYPE_CVWOSTAT_DUM
column.comment: CVWOSTAT is converged Work Order Status, The source is converged status value.
